    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The goal is to implement the API from [@remixproject/engine-web](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-plugin/blob/master/packages/engine/web/src/lib/theme.ts) inside remix-ide.\r\n\r\nThe plugin should: \r\n- Manages 2 themes (light & dark) which implement the [Theme interface](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-plugin/blob/master/packages/api/src/lib/theme/types.ts#L1)\r\n- Implements the methods `currentTheme` & `setTheme`\r\n- Keep the selected theme in localstorage\r\n- Initial theme should be the one from localstorage or \"light\" if none\r\n- emit `themeChanged` event with the new theme inside\r\n\r\nThemes should used the value of the current themes : \r\n- dark: https://res.cloudinary.com/lianahus/raw/upload/v1597918237/remix-themes/PR365/remix-dark_tvx1s2.css\r\n- light: https://res.cloudinary.com/lianahus/raw/upload/v1597918237/remix-themes/PR365/remix-light_powaqg.css",
